ComicInfo.Title: The Trap is Sprung!
ComicInfo.Series: Star Wars: The High Republic Adventures
ComicInfo.Summary:
Hidden aboard the Dank Graks ship, Sav, Maz Kanata, and her crew pause to plot their next move, while the villainous Arkik makes preparations to acquire a devastating new weapon. Sav must make an important decision when the deal gets explosive: save her new friends or save her own skin!
